    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.26.30a" />
                
                
                
                <opener>
                <dateline>
                c/o Petri<lb/>
                Route 5,<lb/>
                Columbia, Mo.<lb/>
                Nov. 1, 59
                </dateline>
                
                
                <salute>Dear Slade:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>I have nothing new to say, but I feel an urge to tell you I am thinking of you and that you are dear to me.</p>
                
                <p>My classes are a source of pleasure, as usual. Our weather is perfect &#8212; golden days and colored leaves, with a tang of frost.
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.26.30b"/>
                <fw type="authorial">-2-</fw>
                    <fw type="curatorial"><del/></fw>
                
                I'm writing this at Skryim, which I don't like to leave; but I must have the water shut off and the pipes drained.</p> 
                <closer>
                <salute>Kindest thoughts for Nita</salute>
                
                <salute>Love always,</salute>
                <signed>John N.</signed>
                </closer>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">30</fw>
            </div1>
        </body>
        
